If you have a favorite small biz, I highly recommend (a) finding
out where they=E2=80=99re based, and (b) sending them an email when
you=E2=80=99re in town.

[PSA: Learn UI Design (
https://click.convertkit-mail.com/v8uownqnkvcrhqq0pgsg/owhkhqh4oo2zv6uv/aHR=
0cHM6Ly9sZWFybnVpLmRlc2lnbg=3D=3D
